text: Bjarne Ansbøl (born 3 July 1937) is a Danish wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman welterweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Danish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Denmark Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Copenhagen
